FBIS4-9669 "drlat062_m_94004" FBIS-LAT-94-062 Daily Report 30 Mar 1994 Brazil Alexander Dupeyrat Named New Justice Minister Alexander Dupeyrat Named New Justice Minister PY3003235494 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network in Portuguese 2200 GMT 30 Mar 94 PY3003235494 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network Portuguese BFN [Text] Presidential special adviser Alexander Dupeyrat is the new justice minister. He is replacing Mauricio Correa, who will run in the next elections. This was confirmed today by President Itamar Franco in Planalto Palace. He also said he has yet not chosen who will replace Labor Minister Walter Barelli, who is stepping down from his post to run for an electoral post.
